# ⚠️ MANDATORY: Read These Files BEFORE Any Task
# RFQ Buddy — Zed Agent Rules
# Auto-loaded by Zed for every agent interaction in this project.

---

## STEP 1 — Read These Files First (in order)

Before doing ANYTHING, read these three files:

1. `/rules.md` — Generic multi-agent coordination rules
2. `/rfq-buddy-rules.md` — Project-specific rules  
3. `/skills/README.md` — Skills system overview

**Do not proceed with any task until all three are read.**

---

## STEP 2 — Select Skills

Based on your task, apply the correct skill(s):

| Task | Required Skill(s) |
|------|-------------------|
| New feature / multi-file change | `plan_before_code` |
| Bug fix | `root_cause_debugging` + `surgical_execution` |
| Backend/shared module change | `architecture_respect` + `surgical_execution` |
| Auth, migrations, billing, bids | `high_risk_change_guard` (mandatory) |

**State your selected skills explicitly before proceeding.**

Skill files at: `/skills/plan_before_code.md`, `/skills/root_cause_debugging.md`, `/skills/surgical_execution.md`, `/skills/architecture_respect.md`, `/skills/high_risk_change_guard.md`

