## CRITICAL PROJECT FACTS

### Database spelling — non-negotiable
```
✅ organizations, organization_id    ← CORRECT (American spelling)
❌ organisations, organisation_id    ← WRONG — will cause SQL errors
```

### Architecture — strict top-down only
```
Routes → Middleware → Controllers → Services → Database
```

### Migration numbering
- Migrations 001–014 exist
- **Next migration: 015**
- Every migration MUST have matching `_rollback.sql`

### Protected files (extend only, never rewrite)
- `backend/src/services/tenderTypeSelector.service.ts`

### Documentation locations
- Phase reports → `/plans/phases/`
- Testing reports → `/plans/testing/`
- Analysis → `/plans/reports/`

---

## Verification (after every change)

```powershell
cd backend && npm run build && npm run lint && npm test
cd frontend && npm run build && npm run check
```

